description: The compilers of the Barrington Atlas associate this place named "Pikrai Limnai" with Lake Timsah, a lake also known as "Crocodile Lake". Lake Timsah is located approximately nine miles (14 km) from the Bitter Lakes.
details: The Barrington Atlas Directory notes: Lake Timsah
